<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="appeal-n">appeal <strong><em>n</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /ə'piːl/    美 /ə'piːl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c-u">1.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 呼吁；恳请：</strong></h4>
<ul>
<li>appeal (to sb) for sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>make / <strong>launch</strong> an <strong>appeal</strong> for money and clothes
呼吁捐钱捐衣物</p></div>

<ul>
<li>appeal to sb to do sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The organization has <strong>launched an appeal to</strong> the public to raise £150,000 for the sick kid<strong> to_2</strong>
这个组织呼吁公众筹集15万英镑以拯救这个生病的孩子。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-u">2.★ <strong>[U] 吸引力；魅力：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>have / hold <strong>wide</strong> / <strong>popular appeal</strong>
广受欢迎</p></div>

<ul>
<li>appeal for sb:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Small cars are economical of fuel, so they have more appeal for consumers.
小型车油耗低，因而更受消费者青睐。</p></div>

<h4 id="3c-u">3.<strong>[C] &amp; [U] 上诉；申诉；上诉权：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>lose an appeal
上诉失败</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The sentence was reduced to three years <strong>on appeal</strong>.
通过上诉，刑期减为三年。</p></div></div>